                    </div>
                    <span>I found this book to be entertaining and very easy to read. Franklins personality is brought to life both in his accomplishments and failures in his family life. I thought it was amazing how much one person could accomplish. The level of detail was exactly what I was looking for.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">A decent protrayal, but not very interesting</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
